                "text": " Assigns the specified roles to the given resource, granting it the necessary permissions on the target Azure Key Vault resource. This replaces the default role assignments for the resource. "
              }
            ],
            "remarks": [
              {
                "kind": "text",
                "text": " Assigns the KeyVaultReader role to the 'Projects.Api' project. "
              },
              {
                "kind": "codeblock",
                "text": "\n             var builder = DistributedApplication.CreateBuilder(args);\n            \n             var vault = builder.AddAzureKeyVault(\"vault\");\n             \n             var api = builder.AddProject<Projects.Api>(\"api\")\n               .WithRoleAssignments(vault, KeyVaultBuiltInRole.KeyVaultReader)\n               .WithReference(vault);\n             ",
                "language": "csharp"
              }
            ],
            "returns": [
